summary: Relating to Personnel; amending Seattle Municipal Code Sections 4.20.190, 4.20.210, 4.20.250, and 4.68.110; and repealing Seattle Municipal Code Sections 4.20.100, 4.20.260, 4.20.270, 4.20.330, 4.20.520, 4.20.530, 4.20.540, 4.20.550 and 4.34.040, to delete references to salary and vacation provisions for employees covered by collective bargaining agreements.
